name: Demographic Analyses
description: Moments before the destruction of his ship Rodani Mihra attempted to destroy these files. The formatting procedure didn't fully complete before his ship was downed, however, and fragments of data remain, including one important-looking document. Highly convoluted and riddled with economic terminology, it appears to be a comprehensive report on various regions. Each and every system has been broken down into demographic sub-groups that clearly outline where the demand for illegal boosters is currently greatest and where it is mostly likely to grow in the coming weeks and months.
